abstract: New York Red Bulls defeat Chicago Fire, 2-1, in MLS action.
lead_paragraph: Sacha Kljestan had a goal and an assist as the Red Bulls ended a 14-game winless streak at Chicago and earned their second Supporters’ Shield in three seasons.

headline.main: Road Win Gives the Red Bulls Another Regular-Season Title
